I"v<p>The 2022 American Conference of Information Systems (AMCIS) is taking place from August 10 through August 14, 2022, in Minneapolis, Minnesota. AMCIS 2022 brings together information systems researchers from around the world to discuss cutting-edge research through exciting workshops, ancillary meetings, research presentations and keynotes. AMCIS 2022 also features events for those at all stages of their academic careers, including Doctoral Consortia, a Junior Faculty Consortium, and a Mid-Career Consortium.</p>

<p>Register for AMCIS 2022 at <a href="https://amcis2022.aisconferences.org/register/"> AMCIS 2022 </a>.</p>
